{DIALOGUE}: You had better be careful.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Big Chris starts his car up, looks across to make sure that Little Chris has got his seatbelt on and pulls out on to the road.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He gets faster and faster until Dog pokes him in the shoulder with his knife.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Chris pulls hard to the left and rams into the nearest parked vehicle.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BANG' Dog goes flying forward, hitting the windscreen.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. ED'S CAR (STATIC) OUTSIDE HATCHET HARRY'S OFFICE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Another time lapse.
